      "x": 1260,
      "y": 740,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 310,
      "text": "WER NUTZT WAS:\n\n/ideation\n  · ARCHITECTURE_DESIGN.md (lesen)\n  · architecture-dimensions.md\n  · specs/TEMPLATE.md (schreiben)\n\n/implement\n  · ARCHITECTURE_DESIGN.md + ADRs\n  · governance-validation.md\n  · spec-gate.sh · doc-version-sync.sh\n  · change-checklist.md\n\n/architecture-review + /sprint-review\n  · ALLE Gruppe-A-Dokumente (lesen)\n  · Journal-Logs (LEARNINGS · STRATEGY)\n\n/security-architect\n  · SECURITY.md (schreiben)\n  · OWASP · ASVS · MITRE ATLAS Refs",
